## 🎯 Quick Reference: When to Use What

| Scenario | Search Method | Why |
|----------|---------------|-----|
| "Find TC_001" | BM25 | Exact ID matching, instant |
| "How do I share reports?" | Vector | Natural language, semantic |
| "Share or send or distribute reports" | Hybrid | Mix keyword + semantic |
| "Find most relevant to my needs" | Score Fusion | LLM reranking |
| "Need module + concept match" | Hybrid + Filters | Combined + metadata |
| "Very specific keywords" | BM25 Heavy | Keyword-focused |
| "Conceptual search" | Vector Heavy | Meaning-focused |

